Description: Real-time system monitoring tool with frequency control
 System Monitor Tool provides real-time monitoring of CPU, GPU, NPU,
 and memory usage with a graphical user interface built on PyQt5.
 .
 Features include:
  * Real-time CPU usage and frequency monitoring
  * GPU monitoring (Intel, NVIDIA, and AMD support)
  * NPU monitoring (Intel and other platform-specific)
  * Memory and swap usage tracking
  * CPU frequency and governor control
  * Historical data logging to SQLite database
  * Low-overhead design for minimal system impact
